Ordering at a coffee shop. Good morning. Can I get a coffee, please?
在咖啡店点单。早上好，可以给我来杯咖啡吗？

3
00:00:18,140 --> 00:00:20,230
Good morning
早上好。

4
00:00:20,870 --> 00:00:21,870
Absolutely
