5
00:00:21,870 --> 00:00:27,550
What type of coffee would you like? I'll have a cappuccino, please
您要什么类型的咖啡呢？我要一杯卡布奇诺。

6
00:00:29,960 --> 00:00:31,960
medium-sized if possible
如果有的话，中杯的。

7
00:00:33,750 --> 00:00:35,270
sure thing
好的，没问题。

8
00:00:35,270 --> 00:00:41,690
Would you like it for here or to go? I'll have it to go, please
是堂食还是外带呢？请帮我打包带走吧。

9
00:00:44,010 --> 00:00:46,010
Alright anything else
还需要别的吗？

10
