Just the cappuccino and the muffin, please
就是卡布奇诺和玛芬，谢谢。

13
00:01:06,780 --> 00:01:09,380
Alright, that will be eight dollars
好的，一共八美元。

14
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:12,170
cash or card
现金还是刷卡呢？

15
00:01:12,210 --> 00:01:15,530
